  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::EndingCard
  panelText: {fileID: 1978720690}
  textToSet: "- Higher cost of living = More women needed to work\r\n\r\n- More women
    work = more men need to be more nurturing and emotionally sensitive to take care
    of children\r\n\r\n- More women work = Greater power in relationship \r\n\r\n-
    More power in a relationship = more women demand that men be less authoritative
    and empathetic\r\n\r\n- More women also like softer traits like being a good
    listener -> Companies make money by appealing to this (E.g music companies)\r\n\r\n-
    Appeal for softer masculinity also grows from such influence\r\n"
