  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::EndingCard
  panelText: {fileID: 1978720690}
  textToSet: '- Growing popularity of South Korean (SK) culture

    

    - More
    women consume them. More women become affluent. More demand for such media

    

    -
    More income = more likely to travel

    

    - Chinese people who go to SK
    deepen their love for SK culture

    

    - Chinese men richer = more focus
    on grooming

    

    - Grooming habits influenced by wives/girlfriends who
    also tend to like SK idols

    

    - Increase in demand for SK culture =
    more SK culture values exported to China = greater appeal for softer masculinity

'
